    <p>Generative Engine Optimization emerged as a distinct discipline in late 2023, following the widespread adoption of ChatGPT and the launch of AI-powered search experiences such as Perplexity and Bing Chat.</p>
    
    <h2>Key Milestones</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>2022–2023</strong>: Rise of ChatGPT and public awareness of LLMs</li>
      <li><strong>2023</strong>: First research paper on GEO published by Princeton researchers</li>
      <li><strong>2024</strong>: Major platforms begin surfacing citations in AI answers</li>
      <li><strong>2025–2026</strong>: GEO becomes a core competency for content teams</li>
    </ul>
